name: Leonid laitskyi
details: The biologist Leonid Laitskyi is a assistant professior at the Institute of advanced Studies at the University of Strasbourg, and a research director at the CNRS. He was awarded the nobel prize in Medicine in 2011 for her research on innate immunity
